710971f-a.title: Manhattan: 8th Street (East) - Avenue D
710971f-a.text:
(1)
East 8th Street, north side, east from, but not including Ave. D.,
to the East River. Also shown is Pier No. 60, East River, eastern ex-
tension of East 8th Street. Note the beginning of Lewis Street, on the
right.
September 16, 1935.
P. L. SPerr.
(2)
The same, but viewed in the opposite direction.
Soptember 11, 1935.
P. L. Serr.
